<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-74-0080 </DOCNO><TEXT>In the dissenting opinion of one of the judges of the Bavarian ConstitutionalCourt concerning the decision of August 14, 1987, the Land Bavaria hasa competence according to the constitution to decide about sites of nuclearinstallations. Hence it follows that a referendum on this problem hasto be permitted. (CW)</TEXT></DOC>